Responsibilities:
Achieve Flow Business Unit booking goals for Lifecycle Services for the Oil & Gas, Chemical and Petrochemical cluster accounts in Southeast Asia & Taiwan.
Collaborate with Flow Industry Solutions Group to drive technology adoption in the respective Accounts.
Generate additional business opportunities with effective utilization of flow service center/calibration lab.
Develop and execute Lifecycle Service account plan for installed bases in Southeast Asia & Taiwan.
Provide accurate and punctual forecasting reports (POR) on a monthly basis to support achieving business goals.
Develop strong relationship with end-users to build strong advocates in their organization and to help create a differentiated vision.
Develop a keen understanding of strategic imperatives and pains impacting the site and formulate targeted solutions around customer pains; develop site account plan for key accounts
